addVoter(address).details: addVoter function use the onlyOwner modifier to restrict this action to Owner.

constructor.details: constructor integration to allow directly Smart Contract deployer to interact with the Dapp.

getVoter(address).details: getVoter() and getOneProposals() functions allow voters to get informations about voters or proposals (by voter address and proposal Id).

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

startProposalsRegistering().details: States functions witch wll be activated by Owner to orchestrate the vote process. Without activation, nobody will be able to interact with wrong status's functions and an error  message will be send to the msg.sender.

tallyVotes().details: The winning proposal Id will be directly caught in the setVote function to prevent DoS gas limit attack.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

_winningProposalId.details: Voters can't vote twice. Also we decided to implement a private variable _winingproposalId here to prevent DoS gas limit attack in the TallyVote() function in case of malicious proposals.

devdoc.title: Voting.sol secure and optimized Smart Contract

VoterRegistered(address).notice: These different events will be emitted in their appropriate function.

addProposal(string).notice: ProposalsRegistrationStarted is the second stage of the voting process. Voters will be able to add as musch proposals thez wants.

addVoter(address).notice: RegisteringVoters is the fisrt stage of the voting process. $ The owner will add the voters address manually in this stage. A voter address can't be added twice.

tallyVotes().notice: VotingSessionEnded is the fourth stage of the voting process. OnlyOwner will be able to reveal the winning proposal Id.

winningProposalID().notice: WinningProposalId will show the final result in the TallyVote function. (numbers of proposals would be adapted for a smal community like here)

workflowStatus().notice: WorkflowStatus will define the current state of voting process.

userdoc.notice: Voting.sol Smart Contract allow registered voters to add as musch proposals  they want to finally vote for their favorite. The Owner will specify the different states of voting status.
